BT /F2 16 Tf 54 744 Td (1. What GitHub Copilot Is) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 718 Td (GitHub Copilot is an AI programming assistant. In VS Code, it can suggest code as you type, answer) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 704.8 Td (questions about files, explain errors, help write tests, propose refactors, and carry out multi-step) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 691.6 Td (tasks when used in agentic modes. It works best when you give it a clear task and enough project) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 678.4 Td (context.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 661.2 Td (Copilot is not one feature. It is a collection of related features:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 644 Td (- Code completions: suggestions that appear while you type.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 630.8 Td (- Chat: a conversational panel for questions and tasks.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 617.6 Td (- Inline chat and inline editing: prompts entered directly in the editor.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 604.4 Td (- Edit mode: targeted code changes to selected files or regions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 591.2 Td (- Agent mode: multi-step work where Copilot can inspect files, propose edits, and sometimes run) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 578 Td (commands or tools with approval.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 564.8 Td (- Custom instructions: persistent rules that tell Copilot how to work in a project.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 551.6 Td (- MCP tools: external context and actions exposed through Model Context Protocol servers.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 538.4 Td (For students, the danger is using Copilot as a replacement for thinking. If you ask, "Write my) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 525.2 Td (assignment," you may get code that seems plausible but does not match the lesson, the style) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 512 Td (requirements, the hidden tests, or your own understanding. A better request is: "Help me design a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 498.8 Td (plan for this assignment. Ask me clarifying questions first. Do not write the final code yet.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 481.6 Td (Copilot is strongest when you already have a direction. It can reduce friction, explain unfamiliar) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 468.4 Td (syntax, generate examples, and help you get unstuck. It is weakest when the task is vague, the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 455.2 Td (context is missing, or you accept the first answer without review.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 438 Td (A productive mental model is:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 420.8 Td (- You are the driver.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 407.6 Td (- Copilot is the navigator and assistant.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 394.4 Td (- The compiler, tests, and course requirements are the judge.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 381.2 Td (When these disagree, do not trust the most fluent answer. Investigate.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 359 Td (Classroom Rule) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 333 Td (Any submitted code must be code you can explain. If Copilot produced a function, you should be able) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 319.8 Td (to describe its inputs, outputs, control flow, edge cases, and tests. If you cannot explain it, you) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 306.6 Td (have not finished learning from it.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 54 30 Td (GitHub Copilot Tutorial for Students  |  3) Tj ET
endstream
