BT /F2 16 Tf 54 744 Td (2. Setup in VS Code) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 718 Td (Before using Copilot, make sure your environment is ready.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 700.8 Td (1. Install Visual Studio Code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 687.6 Td (2. Sign in to GitHub from VS Code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 674.4 Td (3. Install or enable the GitHub Copilot and GitHub Copilot Chat extensions if your VS Code) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 661.2 Td (installation does not include them.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 648 Td (4. Open a folder, not just a single file, so Copilot can see project context.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 634.8 Td (5. Confirm your course repository is open and trusted.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 621.6 Td (In a student workflow, you usually want one VS Code window per assignment repository. This gives) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 608.4 Td (Copilot a clearer workspace and keeps context from different projects from mixing together.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 591.2 Td (Recommended layout:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 574 Td (- Explorer on the left.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 560.8 Td (- Editor in the center.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 547.6 Td (- Terminal at the bottom.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 534.4 Td (- Copilot Chat in the secondary sidebar or panel.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 521.2 Td (- Source Control view available for reviewing changes.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 508 Td (Good setup also includes a working test command. For example:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 487.8 Td (npm test) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 475.8 Td (pytest) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 463.8 Td (mvn test) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 451.8 Td (dotnet test) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 439.8 Td (cargo test) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 424.8 Td (If you do not know how to run the project, ask Copilot in Ask mode:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 404.6 Td (Look at this repository and tell me how to run the tests. Do not change files.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 389.6 Td (Then verify the answer in the README, package files, build files, or course instructions. Copilot) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 376.4 Td (may infer a command that is common but wrong for your specific repository.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 354.2 Td (First Safety Habit) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 328.2 Td (Before asking Copilot to edit code, check Git status:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 308 Td (git status) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 293 Td (Know what changed before and after AI assistance. In VS Code, use the Source Control view to inspect) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 279.8 Td (every modification. Never commit generated code that you have not reviewed.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 54 30 Td (GitHub Copilot Tutorial for Students  |  4) Tj ET
endstream
