BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 525.2 Td (Use Ctrl+Shift+P when:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 508 Td (- A keyboard shortcut is different on your machine.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 494.8 Td (- A Copilot button is hidden.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 481.6 Td (- You want to discover related commands.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 468.4 Td (- You need to reset, reload, or configure VS Code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 455.2 Td (The Command Palette matters because it teaches you the names of actions. Once you know the command) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 442 Td (name, you can find documentation, assign a custom shortcut, or ask Copilot about it precisely.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 424.8 Td (Weak prompt:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 404.6 Td (Copilot is not working.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 389.6 Td (Better prompt:) Tj ET
