BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 357.4 Td (    but the chat panel did not appear. What should I check next? Ask me for version or sign-in) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 345.4 Td (    details if needed.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 330.4 Td (The better prompt gives Copilot the exact action, expected result, actual result, and permission to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 317.2 Td (ask clarifying questions.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 295 Td (Practice) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 269 Td (Open the Command Palette and search for Copilot. Do not run every command. Read the names. Notice) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 255.8 Td (which actions are about chat, which are about completions, which are about fixes, and which are) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 242.6 Td (about settings.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 54 30 Td (GitHub Copilot Tutorial for Students  |  5) Tj ET
