BT /F2 16 Tf 54 744 Td (5. Code Completions) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 718 Td (Code completions are suggestions that appear as you type. They are different from chat. A completion) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 704.8 Td (is usually based on the current file, nearby code, comments, names, and project context.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 687.6 Td (Completions are helpful for:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 670.4 Td (- Repetitive code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 657.2 Td (- Boilerplate.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 644 Td (- Common syntax.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 630.8 Td (- Test cases that follow an existing pattern.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 617.6 Td (- Small helper functions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 604.4 Td (Completions are risky for:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 587.2 Td (- Security-sensitive code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 574 Td (- Authentication and authorization.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 560.8 Td (- Database queries.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 547.6 Td (- Concurrency.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 534.4 Td (- Numerical algorithms.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 521.2 Td (- Code you do not understand.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 508 Td (To get better completions, write clear names and comments before the code. Copilot responds strongly) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 494.8 Td (to surrounding context.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 477.6 Td (Poor setup:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 457.4 Td (def f\(x\):) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 445.4 Td (    pass) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 430.4 Td (Better setup:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 410.2 Td (def normalize_email\(raw_email: str\) -> str:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 398.2 Td (    """Return a lowercase, stripped email address. Raise ValueError if missing @.""") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 383.2 Td (Now Copilot has a name, type information, behavior, and error rule. The resulting suggestion is more) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 370 Td (likely to be useful.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 352.8 Td (Do not accept large completions blindly. Accept a few lines, read them, then continue. If a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 339.6 Td (suggestion is wrong, reject it and write more context yourself. You are allowed to guide the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 326.4 Td (assistant by writing better code around it.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 304.2 Td (Practice) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 278.2 Td (Create a small function with a descriptive name and docstring. Pause and watch the completion. Then) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 265 Td (reject it and rewrite the docstring with clearer constraints. Notice how the suggestion changes.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 54 30 Td (GitHub Copilot Tutorial for Students  |  7) Tj ET
endstream
