BT /F2 16 Tf 54 744 Td (6. Ask Mode) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 718 Td (Ask mode is for conversation and explanation. It should be your default when you are uncertain. In) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 704.8 Td (Ask mode, Copilot answers without directly changing your files unless you explicitly move into an) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 691.6 Td (editing flow.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 674.4 Td (Use Ask mode for:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 657.2 Td (- Understanding an error message.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 644 Td (- Explaining unfamiliar code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 630.8 Td (- Comparing two approaches.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 617.6 Td (- Asking what command runs tests.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 604.4 Td (- Learning a library concept.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 591.2 Td (- Requesting a plan before implementation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 578 Td (- Reviewing a solution you wrote yourself.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 564.8 Td (Good Ask mode prompt:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 544.6 Td (I am learning recursion. Explain this function step by step using the input [1, 2, 3]. Do not) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 532.6 Td (    rewrite the code yet. After explaining, ask me one question to check my understanding.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 517.6 Td (Ask mode is excellent for small models because many questions do not require the most expensive or) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 504.4 Td (most powerful model. A small or fast model is usually enough for definitions, syntax explanations,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 491.2 Td (short examples, and quick comparisons. Save larger models for tasks where reasoning quality matters) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 478 Td (more.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 460.8 Td (Ask mode is also the safest mode for academic integrity. It lets you learn without immediately) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 447.6 Td (generating a final answer. When in doubt, ask Copilot to teach, question, or review rather than) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 434.4 Td (solve.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 412.2 Td (Ask Mode Guardrails) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 386.2 Td (Useful guardrails:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 369 Td (- "Do not write the final code.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 355.8 Td (- "Ask me clarifying questions first.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 342.6 Td (- "Explain using beginner-friendly language.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 329.4 Td (- "Point to the exact line that causes the error.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 316.2 Td (- "Give hints in three levels, from subtle to direct.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 303 Td (- "Use the concepts from this week's lesson only.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 289.8 Td (These guardrails keep the interaction educational.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 54 30 Td (GitHub Copilot Tutorial for Students  |  8) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
