stream
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 744 Td (7. Edit Mode and Inline Editing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 718 Td (Edit mode is for targeted changes. Instead of merely answering, Copilot proposes edits to files.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 704.8 Td (Inline editing is the smaller version of this idea: you select code, ask for a change, and review) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 691.6 Td (the diff.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 674.4 Td (Use Edit mode for:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 657.2 Td (- Refactoring a function.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 644 Td (- Adding input validation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 630.8 Td (- Writing tests for an existing module.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 617.6 Td (- Updating names for clarity.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 604.4 Td (- Fixing a localized bug.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 591.2 Td (- Converting a loop to a clearer structure.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 578 Td (Do not use Edit mode when you have not decided what should change. If the problem is still vague,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 564.8 Td (use Ask mode or planning first.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 547.6 Td (Good edit prompt:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 527.4 Td (In `src/cart.py`, update `calculate_total` so it ignores inactive items and applies the discount) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 515.4 Td (    after tax. Preserve the public function signature. Add or update unit tests. Do not change) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 503.4 Td (    unrelated files.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 488.4 Td (Notice the ingredients:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 471.2 Td (- File name.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 458 Td (- Function name.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 444.8 Td (- Desired behavior.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 431.6 Td (- Constraint on public API.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 418.4 Td (- Test instruction.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 405.2 Td (- Scope guardrail.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 392 Td (After Copilot proposes edits, review the diff. Ask:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 374.8 Td (- Did it change only the intended files?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 361.6 Td (- Did it preserve names and interfaces required by tests?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 348.4 Td (- Did it add unnecessary dependencies?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 335.2 Td (- Did it handle edge cases?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 322 Td (- Did it update or add tests?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 308.8 Td (- Can I explain every changed line?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 295.6 Td (If the answer is no, do not accept the edit as finished. Ask for a smaller change or manually) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 282.4 Td (correct it.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 260.2 Td (Inline Editing Prompt Pattern) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 234.2 Td (Use:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 214 Td (Change [specific code] so that [desired behavior]. Keep [constraints]. Do not [forbidden) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 202 Td (    changes]. Add [tests or comments only if needed].) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 187 Td (This pattern prevents broad, surprising rewrites.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 54 30 Td (GitHub Copilot Tutorial for Students  |  9) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
