stream
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 744 Td (11. Model Selection Checklist) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 718 Td (Before choosing a model, ask four questions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 700.8 Td (First, how much reasoning is required? If the task involves tradeoffs, hidden dependencies, or) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 687.6 Td (multiple files, use a stronger model. If it is a short factual or syntax question, use a smaller) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 674.4 Td (one.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 657.2 Td (Second, how much context is required? If Copilot must understand a large repository, a model with a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 644 Td (larger context window may help. But more context can also distract the model if you include) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 630.8 Td (irrelevant files.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 613.6 Td (Third, what is the cost or quota impact? Some models consume more credits or premium requests.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 600.4 Td (Students should learn to budget model use. Do not spend a large model on questions a small model can) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 587.2 Td (answer.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 570 Td (Fourth, what is the risk of being wrong? A wrong explanation in a practice exercise is easy to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 556.8 Td (correct. A wrong security fix, migration plan, or database change is expensive. Higher risk) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 543.6 Td (justifies stronger reasoning and more human review.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 521.4 Td (Recommended Defaults) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 495.4 Td (For this class:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 478.2 Td (- Ask mode default: small or fast model.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 465 Td (- Edit mode default: medium coding model.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 451.8 Td (- Agent mode default: medium model for routine tasks, large model for hard tasks.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 438.6 Td (- Plan-first prompt: large model.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 425.4 Td (- Security review: large model, plus human review and tests.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 412.2 Td (- Final polish or formatting: small or medium model.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 399 Td (Do not rely only on model names. Providers and model families change. Look at the model picker,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 385.8 Td (course policy, and GitHub's supported model documentation. If a model is retired or unavailable,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 372.6 Td (choose the closest available size and capability.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 350.4 Td (Important Habit) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 324.4 Td (When switching models, tell Copilot why:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 304.2 Td (Use a planning-oriented answer. I am selecting a larger model because this is a multi-file) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 292.2 Td (    design task. Do not write code yet.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 277.2 Td (This gives the model a role and reduces the chance it jumps into implementation too early.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 54 30 Td (GitHub Copilot Tutorial for Students  |  13) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
