stream
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 744 Td (12. Prompt Design: Context, Instructions, Guardrails) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 718 Td (A strong prompt has three parts:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 700.8 Td (- Context: what Copilot needs to know.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 687.6 Td (- Instructions: what you want done.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 674.4 Td (- Guardrails: what must not happen or what constraints must be followed.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 661.2 Td (Weak prompt:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 641 Td (Fix this.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 626 Td (Strong prompt:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 605.8 Td (Context: This is a Flask route that handles new user registration. The failing test says) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 593.8 Td (    duplicate emails should return HTTP 409.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 581.8 Td () Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 569.8 Td (Instructions: Find the cause and update the route so duplicate emails are rejected.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 557.8 Td () Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 545.8 Td (Guardrails: Do not change the database schema. Do not remove tests. Keep the JSON response) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 533.8 Td (    format used by the existing error handlers. Add a focused unit test if one is missing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 518.8 Td (Context tells Copilot where it is. Instructions tell it what to do. Guardrails prevent accidental) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 505.6 Td (damage.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 488.4 Td (Good context can include:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 471.2 Td (- The assignment requirement.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 458 Td (- File names.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 444.8 Td (- Error messages.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 431.6 Td (- Test output.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 418.4 Td (- Relevant code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 405.2 Td (- Data examples.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 392 Td (- Course constraints.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 378.8 Td (- What you already tried.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 365.6 Td (Good instructions include:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 348.4 Td (- "Explain.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 335.2 Td (- "Plan.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 322 Td (- "Refactor.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 308.8 Td (- "Implement.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 295.6 Td (- "Write tests.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 282.4 Td (- "Compare options.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 269.2 Td (- "Review for bugs.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 256 Td (Good guardrails include:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 238.8 Td (- "Do not edit files yet.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 225.6 Td (- "Do not add dependencies.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 212.4 Td (- "Use beginner-level Python.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 199.2 Td (- "Keep the public API unchanged.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 186 Td (- "Use only topics covered in class.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 172.8 Td (- "Ask questions if requirements are unclear.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 159.6 Td (Prompt design is not about magic wording. It is about making the task unambiguous.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 54 30 Td (GitHub Copilot Tutorial for Students  |  14) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
