stream
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 744 Td (13. Prompt Templates for Students) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 718 Td (Use these templates as starting points. Replace bracketed text with your details.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 695.8 Td (Understanding Code) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 666.8 Td (I am learning [topic]. Explain [file/function] step by step. Use beginner-friendly language. Do) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 654.8 Td (    not rewrite the code. After explaining, identify two edge cases and ask me one comprehension) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 642.8 Td (    question.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 622.8 Td (Debugging) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 593.8 Td (Context: I expected [expected behavior], but I got [actual behavior]. The error message is) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 581.8 Td (    [paste error]. The relevant files are [files].) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 569.8 Td () Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 557.8 Td (Instructions: Help me diagnose the likely cause. Start with a short list of hypotheses, then) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 545.8 Td (    tell me what to inspect first.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 533.8 Td () Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 521.8 Td (Guardrails: Do not edit code yet. Do not guess if the evidence is missing; ask me for the) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 509.8 Td (    missing output.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 489.8 Td (Planning) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 460.8 Td (Create a plan for [task]. Include assumptions, files likely to change, implementation steps,) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 448.8 Td (    edge cases, and tests. Do not write code yet. If the requirements are ambiguous, ask) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 436.8 Td (    clarifying questions first.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 416.8 Td (Editing) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 387.8 Td (Change [file/function] so that [desired behavior]. Preserve [interfaces/style]. Do not) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 375.8 Td (    [forbidden changes]. Add or update tests for [cases]. Keep the diff small.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 355.8 Td (Reviewing) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 326.8 Td (Review this change for correctness, readability, edge cases, and tests. Prioritize bugs over) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 314.8 Td (    style. Do not rewrite the code unless you find a concrete issue.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 294.8 Td (Learning Without Cheating) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 265.8 Td (Give me hints for solving this problem. Start with a conceptual hint, then a more specific hint,) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 253.8 Td (    then pseudocode only if I ask. Do not provide the final code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 238.8 Td (Templates reduce cognitive load. Over time, you should adapt them to the course, language, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 225.6 Td (assignment style.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 54 30 Td (GitHub Copilot Tutorial for Students  |  15) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
