36 0 obj
<< /Length 2543 >>
stream
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 744 Td (14. Giving Copilot the Right Context) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 718 Td (Copilot can use open files, selected code, repository context, chat history, custom instructions,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 704.8 Td (and sometimes tool-provided context. But it does not automatically know everything you know.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 687.6 Td (Good context is relevant, current, and specific.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 670.4 Td (Relevant means you include the files, errors, and requirements that matter. Do not paste the whole) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 657.2 Td (project when one function and one test are enough.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 640 Td (Current means you provide the latest error output after your most recent change. Old error messages) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 626.8 Td (can mislead the assistant.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 609.6 Td (Specific means you name files, functions, inputs, and outputs.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 592.4 Td (Weak context:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 572.2 Td (My tests fail.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 557.2 Td (Better context:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 537 Td (`tests/test_cart.py::test_discount_after_tax` fails. It expected 10.80 but got 10.50. The) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 525 Td (    relevant function is `calculate_total` in `src/cart.py`. The assignment says tax is applied) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 513 Td (    before discount. Explain the likely issue before suggesting edits.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 493 Td (Context Tools in VS Code) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 467 Td (Depending on your VS Code and Copilot version, you may be able to add files, folders, symbols,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 453.8 Td (terminal output, or other context to a prompt. Use these features deliberately. More context is not) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 440.6 Td (always better. A focused prompt with one file and one failing test often beats a vague prompt with) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 427.4 Td (the whole repository.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 405.2 Td (Keep History Relevant) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 379.2 Td (Long chat history can confuse the model. Start a new chat when:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 362 Td (- You changed tasks.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 348.8 Td (- The model is stuck in a wrong assumption.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 335.6 Td (- The conversation includes outdated errors.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 322.4 Td (- You switched from learning to implementation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 309.2 Td (In the new chat, summarize only the useful facts.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 54 30 Td (GitHub Copilot Tutorial for Students  |  16) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
