stream
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 744 Td (17. A Student Workflow for Assignments) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 718 Td (Here is a disciplined workflow for using Copilot on programming assignments.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 695.8 Td (Step 1: Read the Assignment Yourself) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 669.8 Td (Before opening Copilot, identify:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 652.6 Td (- Required inputs and outputs.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 639.4 Td (- Files you are expected to edit.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 626.2 Td (- Concepts the assignment is practicing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 613 Td (- Restrictions on libraries or style.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 599.8 Td (- How the work will be tested.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 581.6 Td (Step 2: Ask for Clarification, Not Code) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 555.6 Td (Prompt:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 535.4 Td (I will paste an assignment description. Summarize the requirements, list ambiguities, and ask) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 523.4 Td (    clarifying questions. Do not write code.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 503.4 Td (Step 3: Request a Plan) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 477.4 Td (Use a large model if available:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 457.2 Td (Create a plan for this assignment. Include data structures, functions, edge cases, and tests.) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 445.2 Td (    Keep the plan appropriate for an introductory programming course.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 425.2 Td (Step 4: Implement in Small Pieces) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 399.2 Td (Use completions or Edit mode for one function at a time. After each change, run tests.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 377 Td (Step 5: Ask for Review) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 351 Td (Prompt:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 330.8 Td (Review my solution for bugs and missing edge cases. Do not rewrite it. Point to specific lines) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 318.8 Td (    and explain the issue.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 298.8 Td (Step 6: Explain It Back) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 272.8 Td (Ask Copilot to quiz you:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 252.6 Td (Ask me five questions about this solution that would prove I understand it.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 237.6 Td (If you cannot answer, keep studying before submitting.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 54 30 Td (GitHub Copilot Tutorial for Students  |  19) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
