stream
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 744 Td (20. Code Review and Academic Integrity) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 718 Td (Copilot can review code, but it does not replace your own review. Use it as a second reviewer.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 700.8 Td (Good review prompt:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 680.6 Td (Review this diff for correctness, edge cases, readability, and tests. Prioritize real bugs. Do) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 668.6 Td (    not comment on style unless it affects maintainability.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 653.6 Td (Ask for severity:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 633.4 Td (Classify findings as high, medium, or low severity. Include file and line references when) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 621.4 Td (    possible.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 606.4 Td (For academic integrity, follow your course policy. If AI assistance is allowed, you should still be) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 593.2 Td (transparent when required. Keep a record of major prompts if your instructor asks for them.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 576 Td (You are responsible for:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 558.8 Td (- Understanding submitted code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 545.6 Td (- Following assignment constraints.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 532.4 Td (- Citing or reporting AI assistance if required.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 519.2 Td (- Avoiding unauthorized collaboration.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 506 Td (- Not submitting generated work you cannot explain.) Tj ET
BT /F2 16 Tf 54 487.8 Td (Better Learning Prompts) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 461.8 Td (Instead of:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 441.6 Td (Solve this assignment.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 426.6 Td (Use:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 406.4 Td (Help me understand the problem and design a plan.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 391.4 Td (Instead of:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 371.2 Td (Write the code for me.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 356.2 Td (Use:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 336 Td (Give me pseudocode and ask me to implement the next step.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 321 Td (Instead of:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 300.8 Td (Make it pass.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 285.8 Td (Use:) Tj ET
BT /F3 9.5 Tf 54 265.6 Td (Explain why the test fails and guide me to the minimal fix.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 250.6 Td (Copilot should accelerate learning, not bypass it.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 54 30 Td (GitHub Copilot Tutorial for Students  |  22) Tj ET
endstream
