BT /F2 16 Tf 54 338.6 Td (Final Advice) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 312.6 Td (Use Copilot to become more deliberate, not less deliberate. Ask for plans. Ask for explanations. Ask) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 299.4 Td (for reviews. Use small models for simple questions, medium models for normal coding, and large) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 286.2 Td (models for planning because planning determines the quality of the work that follows.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 269 Td (The best Copilot users are not people who type the fewest characters. They are people who give clear) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 54 255.8 Td (context, set useful constraints, review carefully, and keep responsibility for the final result.) Tj ET
